OL,4,G1005FSecrets of the Royal Palaces
OL,5,     GHighgrove House, Gloucester, is
OL,6,     Gthe smallest royal residence
OL,7,     Gcurrently in use, with nine
OL,8,     Gbedrooms. It is King Charles's
OL,9,     Gown creation, featuring a garden
OL,10,     Gdescribed as an 'organic oasis'.
